{"tid":2410751,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺拍拖做比人包洗費果方好著數","createTime":"2021-02-17T00:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T14:02:18.000Z","uid":249170,"like":9,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4b0d22698a52385f485696793eb7af407948ca","tid":2410751,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺拍拖做 比另一半包洗費果方好著數<br />\n<br />\n你既洗費比另一半包哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果付出果方唔肯為你出錢 或 AA制 就可以話對方唔夠大方，孤寒，小家，窮撚，充大頭鬼<br />\n<br />\n如果佢一直請開，但請請下之後開口叫返一直受惠既你請返付出果方一次，又可以話佢計住計住，斤斤計較，孤寒度縮<br />\n<br />\n但係被包洗費既永遠都 唔會比人話拎著數，搵人笨柒，孤寒，小家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n古人孔子都有講<br />\n「付出者不應計，受惠者可計到盡」<br />\n所以拍拖一定要做比人包洗費果方，只多偶然1％回贈比對方唔洗等對方出哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fb9e91ebab7ea8458e89c67f658538a7e03bd6","tid":2410751,"uid":130303,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T01:00:13.000Z","msg":"香港肯AA既女仔就俾人吹捧做好女仔<br />\n肯AA既男仔就俾人話姑寒，唔夠愛女朋友<br />\nThis is Hong Kong"},{"pid":"39599c6b6712e8310acd807298359f163b4c860c","tid":2410751,"uid":1697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T01:32:14.000Z","msg":"係咁嫁啦 你自己權衡下叫雞定溝女著數"},{"pid":"deb25cc3c30f7b8369d449732471cfd2925cc97e","tid":2410751,"uid":392181,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:02:01.000Z","msg":"聽到個女仔話比人請開 已經可以入friend zone <br />\n乞衣定做雞？<br />\n話我斤斤計較嘅話直接skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能我唔夠有錢到可以對錢咁大方<br />\n奉勸呢啲女仔直接搵有錢人<br />\n唔好貪人靚仔又要不時嫌人窮"},{"pid":"07abaa826c7fe051451159e4ef2c80389267bdd1","tid":2410751,"uid":249170,"like":1,"disli